{"tid":2292580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猶太手足從德意志帝國集中營來信: 我很好","createTime":"2020-11-19T14:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T16:15:41.000Z","uid":369971,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2877eb48d3e60af60cdd3683a8d8019f5bbbb0","tid":2292580,"uid":369971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"猶太手足:<br />\n很久沒見，你們還好嗎？<br />\n請大家放心，我的生活很好，日耳曼人對我們很好，你們毋須擔心。<br />\n我們被帶到一個營中，這裡的生活並不像外面謠傳般那麼差，沒有遭受毆打、嚴刑迫供甚至是屠殺。相反地這裡的生活十分的好，伙食很好，每餐有菜有肉，每天能做運動，每天有醫生檢查，有充足睡眠，不會被強逼勞動，還長胖了。<br />\n讓你們擔心很對不起，但我和我的同伴們都生活得很快樂，沒有受虐待，你們不用浪費心思救我們了...<br />\n- 1943<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7MlIazgVJNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7MlIazgVJNw&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=1b2a4056\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7MlIazgVJNw</a>"},{"pid":"b925bb51c78a4bf49ffcb4194453b4aa79bd9e50","tid":2292580,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"3封信都同一個pattern<br />\n好心寒"},{"pid":"37c784a6781e58048d4799c3a7ad98fba66d32c9","tid":2292580,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"極權真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d399992346f5919b4b2c1854a48f9abb6ad396","tid":2292580,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4631aafc03765114c3b73e0f68b85166f879c91","tid":2292580,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:02:58.000Z","msg":"<i